Get your hands up.

490
00:26:21.884 --> 00:26:23.669
[commentator 1]
Another left hand by Creed.

491
00:26:23.712 --> 00:26:26.497
Drago waiting, waiting,
cocking that right hand.

492
00:26:28.935 --> 00:26:30.284
Attack him!

493
00:26:32.155 --> 00:26:33.200
[commentator 2] A crushing
right by the Russian!

494
00:26:36.725 --> 00:26:38.597
Get out of there!
Stay away from him!

495
00:26:38.988 --> 00:26:39.989
[thudding]

496
00:26:40.729 --> 00:26:42.557
Get out of there!

497
00:26:42.601 --> 00:26:44.559
[commentator 1] He's
taking some punishment now!

498
00:26:44.603 --> 00:26:45.821
Drago moves him
against the ropes.

499
