above the American.

959
01:11:18.404 --> 01:11:21.625
It's a true case
of David and Goliath here.

960
01:11:21.668 --> 01:11:24.541
It's unbelievable,
the condition of both men,

961
01:11:24.584 --> 01:11:26.151
but the Russian champion...

962
01:11:26.194 --> 01:11:27.544
I must break you.

963
01:11:35.029 --> 01:11:37.249
